{"tid":1547410,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"只屬於真香港人嘅歌","createTime":"2019-09-06T16:03:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T09:21:03.000Z","uid":239492,"like":70,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"37749e428e2fa8eaf26e43400d604060fb44fdc5","tid":1547410,"uid":239492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T16:03:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5YLHM70.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5YLHM70.jpg&h=09efd335&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n麻煩各位如果許可嘅話 背咗首歌佢 然後每日2031停低唱呢首歌 令更多人識同一齊有勇氣唱同發聲。<br />\n<br />\n今日細佬我係旺角行人天橋已經踏出咗第一步 雖然唱得唔好 有啲位未識唱 但係我見到有一兩個手足一齊唱嘅時候 我就更加用力唱 好多謝有份一齊唱呢首歌嘅手足<br />\n<br />\n希望我地可以係煲底相認嘅時候 可以再一齊唱呢首歌<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">願榮光歸香港</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"8b7c1cd0ceee0ec7a4a18dd661f280cc47bbc81e","tid":1547410,"uid":130035,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T16:05:28.000Z","msg":"Pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />平時都會不自覺哼岀來<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a67155bdf0e2f09ced77e22f291281b401764e8","tid":1547410,"uid":54681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T16:06:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bc86c76609e9dd1be6ca30050a6ace7106d34d5","tid":1547410,"uid":239492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T16:09:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4095e305a4c6bab94d4f1f7f2c819ddd466f0be3","tid":1547410,"uid":213352,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T16:10:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1Yw7YiF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1Yw7YiF.jpg&h=e6c84b70&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">聽日呀！冇人講呀 機場見</span>"},{"pid":"a30bc538d3e694c95001766c1931e7440961